{
  "id": "adv_card_skr_04_01",
  "title": "川咲さくら 1話 新曲リリース",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-night.webp",
      "bgName": "office-01-000-night",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――I-UNITYが終了してしばらく経ち",
      "translations": {
        "en": "ㅡㅡA few moments later after I-UNITY",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_04_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "サニピの新曲『SUNNY PEACE for\nYou and Me！』の正式リリースが決定したぞ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "New song of SUNNY PEACE \"SUNNY PEACE for\nYou and Me!\" release date is decided.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 4.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_04_01-skr001.m4a",
      "text": "本当ですか！？　ありがとうございます！\n思い入れのある曲なのでリリースが決まって嬉しいです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Seriously? I appreciate it!\nI'm glad that the release of the song has been decided‚ as it holds special memories.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 11.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_04_01-skr002.m4a",
      "text": "でも、曲が完成したばかりなのに\nもう発売が決まるなんて早過ぎじゃないですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "\"But the song hasn't been long since it's completed‚\nisn't it too soon to decide on the release?\"",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 18.676581461,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_04_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "I-UNITYでのライブがもの凄い反響だったんだ\nおかげでトントン拍子に話が進んだよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The live response on I-UNITY was so good.\nThanks to that‚ things moved forward quickly.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 25.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_04_01-skr003.m4a",
      "text": "そうだったんですね\n私達の歌がそんなに話題になるなんて嬉しいです！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I see.\nI'm glad that our song has become such a sensation!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 30.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_04_01-skr004.m4a",
      "text": "そうだ！　みんなにもこのことを知らせなきゃ！\nそれじゃあ私はこれで――",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's right! We should let everyone know!\nWell‚ I'll go now――",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 38.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_04_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "ちょっと待った\n新曲のリリースに向けてさくらに一つ頼みがあるんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Wait a second‚\nI have one request for Sakura regarding the release of the new song.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 41.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_04_01-skr005.m4a",
      "text": "私にですか？　分かりました、なんでも言って下さい！\n新曲のためならなんでもやります！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "To me? Alright‚ please tell me anything.\nI'll do whatever it takes for the new song!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 50.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_04_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "そう言ってもらえると心強いよ。さくらにはサニピの\nリーダーとしてMVの製作を手伝ってほしいんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thank you for saying that. As the leader of Sunny Peace‚\nI hope Sakura can assist in producing the MV.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 57.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_04_01-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "もちろんいつものスタッフにも協力してもらうが\n今回はさくらのアイデアを中心に出来ないかと思ってな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Of course‚ you've always cooperated with the production team‚\nbut this time‚ I thought we could go with Sakura's ideas as the main concept.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 64.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_04_01-skr006.m4a",
      "text": "私の考えたアイデアが新曲のMVになるんですか？\n面白そうですね！　ぜひやらせて下さい！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "My idea becoming the new song's MV?\nThat sounds amaznig! Please make it happen!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 73.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_04_01-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "それなら明日の午後、俺と打ち合わせをしよう\n一緒にMVの製作会議に出す資料を作るんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Alright‚ let's have a meeting tomorrow afternoon.\nLet's prepare the materials for the MV production meeting together.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 80.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_04_01-skr007.m4a",
      "text": "分かりました！　明日までにアイデアを考えてきます！\n素敵なMVになるように精一杯頑張ります！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Understood! I'll come up with ideas by tomorrow.\nI'll work hard to make it a great MV!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 88.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――翌日",
      "translations": {
        "en": "ㅡㅡThe next day",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 92.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 93.7
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 93.7
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_04_01-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "では打ち合わせを始めよう\nMVのアイデアは考えてきたか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Shall we start the meeting?\nHave you thought of any ideas for the MV?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 96.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 99.5333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_04_01-skr008.m4a",
      "text": "はい！　実は昨日\nサニピのみんなに呼び掛けて話し合ったんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes! Actually‚\nI discussed it with everyone from Sunny Peace yesterday.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 101.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_04_01-skr009.m4a",
      "text": "どんなMVにしたいかアイデアを出し合って\nみんなの意見を私がまとめてきました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We've come up with some ideas for what kind of MV we'd like to do‚\nand I've compiled everyone's opinions.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 108.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 111.2
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_04_01-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "そんなことをしていたのか\nさくらもリーダーらしくなったな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah‚ so you've been doing that.\nSakura has become quite a leader‚ huh?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 113.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 116.1333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_04_01-skr010.m4a",
      "text": "えへへ……\nそれでいくつかアイデアが出たので聞いて下さい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hehe……\nSo‚ some ideas have come up‚ please listen.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 117.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 122.0333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_04_01-skr011.m4a",
      "text": "まずは雫ちゃんの案です。みんなで崖の上に立って\n風に吹かれながら歌うのはどうでしょうか！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "First‚ there's Suzuku's suggestion. How about all of us standing on a cliff‚\nand singing as the wind blows?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 126.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_04_01-skr012.m4a",
      "text": "崖の上で歌う私達をヘリで空撮するんです\n格好いいと思いませんか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Capturing us singing on the cliff from the air with a helicopter.\nDon't you think it would be cool?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 132.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 135.1666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_04_01-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "他のアーティストでもよく見かける映像だな\nちょっとありがちじゃないか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Other artists often do similar videos.\nDon't you think it's too common though?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 138.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 140.8
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 145.8333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_04_01-skr013.m4a",
      "text": "ダメですか……じゃあこれはどうでしょうか！？\n怜ちゃんのアイデアなんですけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Okay then….how about this one?\nIt's Rei-san's idea.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 145.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_04_01-skr014.m4a",
      "text": "モノクロの映像で\n私達は街の中や部屋の中でダンスを踊り続けるんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "In black and white footage‚\nwe dance continuously on the street or inside a room.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 150.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 154.8333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_04_01-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "それはダンスのPVであって\nアイドルのMVとは違うんじゃないか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But isn't that more like a dance MV?\nWon't it be like idol MVs?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 156.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 162.9333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_04_01-skr015.m4a",
      "text": "そ、そうですね……\nじゃ、じゃあ次はこれです！",
      "translations": {
